Package org.biojava.nbio.aaproperties

Class Constraints

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.biojava.nbio.aaproperties.Constraints
  • public class Constraints
extends Object
    This class is used to support the implementation of properties stated in IPeptideProperties. It initializes several values that would be needed for the computation of properties such as

    Molecular weight
    Instability index
    Hydropathy value
    pKa

    Version:
    2011.05.21
    Author:
    kohchuanhock
    See Also:
    IPeptideProperties
